::The Lavacons::

Astral steps back and looks at what the Lavacons and Wheeljack and 
Composer had been building. He smiles. It looked about complete to 
him.

"Are we done?" he asks Wheeljack. There were probably some other 
things to do, but they were at least mostly done.
